#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Minitron-8B-Base.md:103
msgid "Remarks on Metrics"
msgstr "指标说明"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Minitron-8B-Base.md:105
msgid ""
"**exact_match,strict-match**: Only predictions that strictly match the "
"expected final-answer extraction format are counted as correct."
msgstr "**exact_match,strict-match**：只有严格匹配预期最终答案提取格式的预测才被计为正确。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Minitron-8B-Base.md:106
msgid ""
"**exact_match,flexible-extract**: Predictions are evaluated with a more "
"flexible answer extraction rule, which tolerates minor formatting "
"differences as long as the final numeric answer is correct."
msgstr "**exact_match,flexible-extract**：使用更灵活的答案提取规则评估预测，只要最终的数字答案正确，允许微小的格式差异。"

