msgstr "基准结果"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Minitron-8B-Base.md:112
msgid ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base` can be deployed through `vllm-ascend` for online "
"inference and benchmark evaluation.   Actual throughput and latency "
"depend on hardware resources, prompt length, output length, concurrency, "
"and runtime configuration."
msgstr "`Minitron-8B-Base` 可以通过 `vllm-ascend` 部署，用于在线推理和基准评估。实际吞吐量和延迟取决于硬件资源、提示词长度、输出长度、并发量和运行时配置。"

